cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the deployment of 5G networking infrastructure. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper deals with optimizing the locations of backhaul aggregate nodes and wireless backhaul links. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper proposes a deployment framework to jointly optimize the locations of different network components. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a heuristic algorithm to solve the multi-objective integer programming problem. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is another possible category as the paper deals with the deployment of small base stations and machine aggregators.
